Title: Coherent State Quantization of SU(N) Non-Abelian Chern-Simons Particles
Authors: Taejin Lee and Phillial Oh
Comments: 13 pages, Latex File, SNUTP-93-42
Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B319 (1993) 497-504
\\
  We present a new method of formulating the classical theory of $SU(N+1)$
non-Abelian Chern-Simons (NACS) particles for arbitrary $N\geq 1$ using the
symplectic reduction of $CP(N)$ manifold from $S^{2N+1}$. Quantizing the theory
using BRST formulation and coherent state path integral method , we obtain a
quantum mechanical model for $SU(N+1)$ NACS particles.
